{"id": "1445219292927754290", "channel_id": "1445219292927754290", "type": 0, "author_id": "335454645251997717", "author_name": "iwthahe", "author_bot": false, "content": "I was expecting to try the already overly restricted event that favors old players/big payers, but it's okay I thought, nothing wrong with rewarding a supporting player a bit (x3-x5) more, I'll get my share and it is what it is. \nInstead I got hit with a \"Wake up earlier loser xdd\" + a Poopenfarten3000 Realm Mastery wheel that gives an affinity bonus. Are we celebrating as a community here or is it a damn funeral? Screw the useless wheel, what the hell happened with the raid event? I expected it to be bad, turns out it might as well not exist at all for me personally.", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T01:05:30.310000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-02T03:01:39.395000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "A_pinch", "emoji_id": "1432980538536493057", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445219292927754290", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Isn't anniversary supposed to be like a celebratory thing? So far it feels like im getting fisted.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
